    <p>
        Based on our assessments of any likely sustained loss, consistent with our intrinsic value
        discipline, we may manage the risks as follows:
    </p>
    <ul class="disc">
        <li>
            Divest, hold or protect the individual investment impacted;
        </li>
        <li>
            Change the portfolio composition for the long run;
        </li>
        <li>
            Take actions to protect the portfolio.
        </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
