    <p>
        We comply with all obligations under Singapore laws and regulations, including those arising from
        international treaties and UN sanctions. We also comply with the laws and regulations of
        jurisdictions where we have investments or operations.
    </p>
    <div class="contentpage-blockquote-row row highlight-below">
